WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: uz

00:00:00.390 --> 00:00:04.190
Istalgan joylashuv tartibini qurish uchun rasm aslida 
chekkadan chekkaga o‘taveradi, demak,

00:00:04.190 --> 00:00:07.910
keling, ota view dagi mana 
bu padding dan qutilamiz.

00:00:07.910 --> 00:00:10.270
Ajoyib endi rasm chetdan chetga o‘tadi.

00:00:10.270 --> 00:00:12.470
Keling, pastdagi matnni moslashtiramiz.

00:00:12.470 --> 00:00:16.720
Biz barcha qirralar bo‘ylab 16 dp 
xohlayotganimizni ta’kidlab o‘tdik.

00:00:16.720 --> 00:00:20.690
Yaxshi, men 16 dp padding qo‘shishga 
harakat qilib ko‘rdim, lekin 

00:00:20.690 --> 00:00:23.610
biz aslida faqatgina 
 8 dp padding xohlagan edik.

00:00:23.610 --> 00:00:26.820
Demak, biz uni individual qiymatlarga 
bo‘lib chiqishimiz kerak va 

00:00:26.820 --> 00:00:29.420
keyin pastki padding ni 
8dp qilib qo‘yamiz.

00:00:29.420 --> 00:00:33.480
Yaxshi, endi bizda yuqori, chap va o‘ng 
 padding lar 16dp ga teng, ammo 

00:00:33.480 --> 00:00:36.060
bu TextView ning pastki 
 padding i 8dpga teng.

00:00:36.060 --> 00:00:40.610
Ajoyib, endi siz padding ni 16dp qilib 
qo‘yishingiz kerak bo‘lgan oxirgi matn qoldi.

00:00:40.610 --> 00:00:44.460
Ammo, shoshmay turing, bu hozir ikkita 
 TextView lar orasidagi masofani ko‘paytiradi.

00:00:44.460 --> 00:00:47.760
Keling, bu so‘nggi TextView ga 
ham 16 dp padding qo‘shamiz.

00:00:47.760 --> 00:00:50.960
Bu chap tomondagi, pastki va o‘ng tomondagi 
oraliqlarni to‘g‘ri qilib beradi.

00:00:50.960 --> 00:00:54.350
Ammo, hozir bu ikkita TextView lar 
orasida juda ham bo‘sh joy bor, demak, 

00:00:54.350 --> 00:00:57.460
keling, uni individual qiymatlarga bo‘lamiz.

00:00:57.460 --> 00:01:01.650
Va biz mana shu yerda to‘xtaymiz chunki biz bu view da 
bironta ham yuqori padding dan foydalanishni xohlamaymiz.

00:01:01.650 --> 00:01:04.248
Uning yuqorisidagi bu TextView ning 
pastki padding idan 

00:01:04.248 --> 00:01:05.241
to‘g‘ri bo‘sh joy ajratilayapti.

00:01:06.360 --> 00:01:08.090
Ajoyib, demak bu to‘g‘riga o‘xshab ko‘rinayapti.

00:01:08.090 --> 00:01:10.890
Qolib ketayotgan yagona narsa bu biz mana bu oq bo‘sh 

00:01:10.890 --> 00:01:12.440
joydan qutulishimiz kerak.

00:01:12.440 --> 00:01:15.930
Bu ImageView da bizga pastki padding 
kerak emas, demak, keling uni o‘chirib tashlaymiz.

00:01:15.930 --> 00:01:17.920
Hammasi yaxshi ketayapti, biz bu joylashuv 
tartibini qurishni tugatdik.

